#ELLEBeauty: A dry scalp happens when the skin lacks moisture. It often feels tight, itchy, and may show small, dry patches on scalp areas. Dandruff, on the other hand, is linked to excess oil and yeast overgrowth, which leads to larger, oily flakes and sometimes redness. Head to the 🔗 in the bio to figure out how to treat your dry scalp.
